sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>(TLS + Auth)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>HTTP/gRPC
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>Orchestrator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMEval as LMEval Job

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Platform-enforced
        Ingress->>LS: Forward (TLS terminated)<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>vLLM: POST inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LS: Inference response (streaming/non-streaming)
        LS->>PG: Async write inference log<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, Username/password
        LS-->>Ingress: JSON Response
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Milvus: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector Search
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with RAG context)
        Ingress->>LS: Forward HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>Milvus: Vector similarity search<br/>HTTP/gRPC, Token (MILVUS_TOKEN)
        Milvus-->>LS: Matching document chunks
        LS->>vLLM: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>LS: Embedding vectors
        LS->>vLLM: Inference with context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>LS: Augmented response
        LS->>PG: Store conversation state<br/>PostgreSQL/5432
        LS-->>Ingress: JSON Response
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,LMEval: Flow 3: Model Evaluation (TrustyAI LMEval)
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/eval/run
        Ingress->>LS: Forward HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>K8sAPI: Create LMEval Job<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>LS: Job created
        Note over LMEval: Job runs asynchronously
        LMEval->>vLLM: Evaluation queries<br/>HTTP
        vLLM-->>LMEval: Responses
        LMEval-->>K8sAPI: Job complete + results
        LS->>K8sAPI: Poll job status<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>LS: Results
        LS-->>Ingress: Evaluation results
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,FMS: Flow 4: Safety Shield Evaluation
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/safety/run_shield
        Ingress->>LS: Forward HTTP 8321/TCP
        LS->>FMS: Evaluate content safety<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)
        FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict (pass/fail + details)
        LS-->>Ingress: Safety response
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response (TLS)
    end
